{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/about/updash/","webpackCompilationHash":"8561ee03a699e994f323","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Mike Upchurch","author":"Mike Upchurch"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c67fc3bc-fe20-5e8f-9e74-970e75bec5e4","excerpt":"What is it? Updash is a personalized information dashboard for my home. It displays helpful things about my life such as commute time, currently playing musicâ€¦","html":"<h2>What is it?</h2>\n<p>Updash is a personalized information dashboard for my home. It displays helpful things about my life such as commute time, currently playing music, weather, calendar, Instagram photos, etc.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/275e6da5bb35f5c1b12c6d6d90b5cd6a/68b76/updash.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.3254593175853%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"The updash dashboard, displaying personalized information.\"\n        title=\"The updash dashboard, displaying personalized information.\"\n        src=\"/static/275e6da5bb35f5c1b12c6d6d90b5cd6a/e11df/updash.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/275e6da5bb35f5c1b12c6d6d90b5cd6a/5039d/updash.png 250w,\n/static/275e6da5bb35f5c1b12c6d6d90b5cd6a/d19c0/updash.png 500w,\n/static/275e6da5bb35f5c1b12c6d6d90b5cd6a/e11df/updash.png 1000w,\n/static/275e6da5bb35f5c1b12c6d6d90b5cd6a/8e846/updash.png 1500w,\n/static/275e6da5bb35f5c1b12c6d6d90b5cd6a/68b76/updash.png 1905w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">The updash dashboard, displaying personalized information.</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>What did I learn?</h2>\n<p>It is built using Smashing (a Ruby-based framework for quickly constructing dashboards) and runs on a Raspberry Pi connected to a monitor. I had to customize many of the widgets as they were either no longer working or did not exist.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/mupchrch/updash\">View the source on Github.</a></p>\n<h3>Technologies</h3>\n<p><em>Smashing, Ruby, Coffeescript, CSS</em></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"updash","date":"February 02, 2019","description":"A personal information dashboard for my home."}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/about/updash/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/about/upchat/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"upchat"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/about/mikeup.church/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"mikeup.church"}}}}}